{"word":"προσφορά","slug":"προσφορά","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προσφορά, ᾶς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φέρω\">φέρω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘act of bringing <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, in cultic sense <b>sacrificing, offering <a href='B:510 24:17'>Ac 24:17</a>; <a href='B:650 10:10'>Hb 10:10</a>, <a href='B:650 10:14'>14</a>, <a href='B:650 10:18'>18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> aspect: ‘that which is brought’, <b>sacrifice, offering</b> in cultic sense <b><a href='B:510 21:26'>Ac 21:26</a>; <a href='B:520 15:16'>Ro 15:16</a>; <a href='B:560 5:2'>Eph 5:2</a>; <a href='B:650 10:5'>Hb 10:5</a>, <a href='B:650 10:8'>8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προσφιλής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προσφωνέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}